# Girder-client Platform -*- mode: markdown -*-

This image provides :
* girder-client

Basic girder-cli usage:
* To connect to girder instance:
```
export GIRDER_API_KEY=abcdefghijklmopqrstuvwxyz012345678901234
girder-cli --api-url https://girder.example.com:443/api/v1  ...
```

* To upload:
 ```
girder-cli upload 54b6d41a8926486c0cbca367 test_folder --parent-type folder --dry-run
```

For more info see
https://girder.readthedocs.io/en/latest/python-client.html

